title: ARAM team of Sivir, Nid, Ashe, TF, and Morg! :D
body:
On the enemy team! D:

Our only ranged champion was Corki. The rest were Malph, Yorick, Poppy (me), and Kassadin.

Every single enemy did more champ damage than any of us. It was actually legit funny seeing how long we could delay the game, and I'm pretty proud that we held out until 11:33.
